the Kashmir issue with India.
</P>
<P>
He was talking to reporters soon after his arrival from a
week-long visit to the United States and London at the Airport of
Lahore, capital of eastern Punjab province, Sunday morning, the
official Associated Press of Pakistan reported.
</P>
