<P>
NANJING, September 27 (Xinhua) -- The newly established Nanjing
Xiaozhuang Teachers College has enlisted 80 students who will
become primary school teachers after completing a four-year course.
</P>
<P>
They will be the first primary school teachers with bachelor's
degrees in China. Primary school teachers used to graduate after
only two or three years of study.
</P>
<P>
This practice conforms with the trend of future education and
symbolizes a move toward the international standard, said an
official with the Jiangsu Provincial Education Commission. 
</P>
